msgid ""
"If after editing the text in the dialog, you want &kmymoney; to create the "
"database, you will need to complete the other fields in the dialog, as "
"detailed in <link linkend=\"details.database.selectdatabase\">Creating a "
"Database</link> above, and click <guibutton>Create Tables</guibutton>. Note "
"that, except in the case of SQLite, you will need either to include a "
"suitable <literal>CREATE DATABASE</literal> statement as the first command, "
"or have previously issued such a command externally to &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid pärast teksti muutmist dialoogis, et &kappname; looks andmebaasi, "
"tuleb täita ka dialoogi teised väljad, nagu kirjeldatud eespool osas <link "
"linkend=\"details.database.selectdatabase\">Andmebaasi loomine</link>, ja "
"klõpsata nupule <guibutton>Loo tabelid</guibutton>. Pane tähele aga seda, et "
"kui tegu pole just SQLite'iga, tuleb kas esimese käsuna anda sobiv CREATE "
"DATABASE lause või olla seda juba varem teinud väljaspool &kappname;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-database.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warning"
msgstr "Hoiatus"

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:544
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You should be very careful editing the definitions of any of the basic "
#| "tables or views (those with names beginning with 'kmm'). Some changes, "
#| "such as increasing the length of an integer field, may have little "
#| "impact, but you should not remove or change the sequence of any fields, "
#| "or &kappname; may refuse to function, or may corrupt your data."
msgid ""
"You should be very careful editing the definitions of any of the basic "
"tables or views (those with names beginning with '<literal>kmm</literal>'.) "
"Some changes, such as increasing the length of an integer field, may have "
"little impact, but you should not remove or change the sequence of any "
"fields, or &kmymoney; may refuse to function, or may corrupt your data."
msgstr ""
"Kõigi põhiliste tabelite ja vaadete (mille nimede alguses seisab \"kmm\") "
"definitsioonide muutmisel tuleb olla äärmiselt ettevaatlik. Mõni muudatus, "
"näiteks täisarvuvälja pikkuse suurendamine, ei pruugi õieti mingit mõju "
"avaldada, aga kunagi ei tohiks välju eemaldada ega nende järjekorda muuta, "
"sest muidu ei pruugi &kappname; enam töötada või võid oma andmed tõsiselt "
"ära rikkuda."

#. Tag: para
#: details-database.docbook:552
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Whilst adding or removing indexes may improve performance, you should "
#| "also be aware that the opposite may happen. Some knowledge of the "
#| "internal operation of &kappname; may help to get the best performance in "
#| "these circumstances."
msgid ""
"While adding or removing indexes may improve performance, you should also be "
"aware that the opposite may happen. Some knowledge of the internal operation "
"of &kmymoney; may help to get the best performance in these circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Indeksite lisamine või eemaldamine võib küll jõudlust parandada, aga tuleks "
"teada, et võib ka vastupidi juhtuda. Parima tulemuse saavutamseks peaks "
"vähemalt teataval määral olema kursis &kappname; sisemiste operatsioonidega."

